actions.text: Measure called up under motion to suspend rules and pass in House.

official_title: A resolution providing for the concurrence of the House in the Senate amendments, with the amendments of the House to the bill H.R. 14279.

summary.text: Provides that the bill H.R. 14279 to extend the authority for the flexible regulation of interest rates on deposits and accounts in depository institutions, with the Senate amendments, be taken from the Speaker's table, and that the Senate amendments be agreed to with amendments of the House of Representatives.

titles.title: A resolution providing for the concurrence of the House in the Senate amendments, with the amendments of the House to the bill H.R. 14279.
